The paper proposes a novel approach for RUL estimation using Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) and time series embeddings. This falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. Specifically, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are the most likely sub-categories as they cover topics related to RNNs and time series analysis. Additionally, cs.SI (Signal Processing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are also relevant sub-categories as they cover topics related to sensor data analysis and machine health monitoring.
